  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nGeth has an option to provide a separate directory for the freezer db with the `ancient_datadir` option. This allows storing immutable stuff like blocks into a separate directory which makes it easier for home stakers.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nAllow separating long term storage and hot storage. Apologies if this feature already exists, I couldn't find it anywhere in the docs.\r\n",
